snippet.title: Swordship  | Release Date Trailer
snippet.description:
Dodge, duck and turn your enemies’ weapons against them as you speed across the waterways in Swordship. Out on December 5th on PlayStation 4, PlayStation 5, Xbox One, Xbox Series X|S, Nintendo Switch and PC. 

Steam: https://store.steampowered.com/app/1804270/Swordship/ 
GOG.com: https://www.gog.com/game/swordship 

(Coming to GOG.com and Epic Game Store 2023)
